                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def2-27-18551126 t18551126-27-punishment-31"></join>Confined Six Months</rs>
                  </hi>.</p>
               <p>(<hi rend="italic">
Johnson was subsequently sentenced to twelve months' imprisonment upon another indictment, for which see Third Court, Thursday</hi>.)</p>
